{"tid":1437700,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對付柒婆","createTime":"2019-08-09T15:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T15:16:35.000Z","uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad7841de1571550e15dae94550518771b4dd0115","tid":1437700,"uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"佢近日不停將經濟民生問題同示威者行為捆綁 <br />\n等全部人都覺得全因示威者令香港經濟衰退<br />\n呢招一定要拆<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我建議民間記者會加埋文宣 應該將貿易戰既影響放大 將責任轉為外圍經濟不明朗因素 先至令香港經濟下跌<br />\n</span></span> 絕對唔可以俾柒婆得逞 <br />\n一定要俾全香港人睇清楚事實 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地唔係問題既主因！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"9a14b85956b6067b8a3cd45ab75728cd39f9fa59","tid":1437700,"uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:14:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7929f3fb5f401bc3fc3b74e43c3801513105b0c8","tid":1437700,"uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:15:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"76a97fa1e92f675a74661c57c2e64b0fb5aa8141","tid":1437700,"uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5a01c7a3a2125166aecae262092ccf17aaab9a6a","tid":1437700,"uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:15:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"810a2bace911b0a97f26bb2b4ce245dee9513ed7","tid":1437700,"uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:15:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fa14d21b7eadbe1cfbe71b4264b76b8a571653c","tid":1437700,"uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:15:54.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"6244d4d436c2bd85fc8b7669a02b63b7348b0772","tid":1437700,"uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:16:08.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"p